      <span class="faq-q-text">Can I connect other tools besides GSC and DataForSEO?</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="can-i-connect-other-tools-besides-gsc-and-datafors"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. The MCP ecosystem is growing rapidly. Servers exist for Google Analytics, Semrush, Ahrefs, Screaming Frog, Webflow, WordPress, and dozens of other tools. Any service with an API can potentially have an MCP server. Check the <a href="https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/servers">official MCP server registry</a> for the latest list.</p></div></div>
  </div>
